{
  "2224610": {
    "name": "我不背锅",
    "steam_appid": 2224610,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >【日本沉没！新灾难超级火山现已上线】 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/2def671d649909d57b25c00ca8b18062.avif?t=1772080531\" width=600 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《我不背锅》是一款1v5策略派对游戏。你可以扮演地球的角色，释放灾难摧毁人类；或者加入人类团队，化身为世界领袖、工业、媒体、科学家和公众，与地球对抗，争取生存。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/c20adae35f41667ab0551ca809d79310.webp?t=1772080531\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为地球，你的目标是摧毁人类以确保自己的生存。选择各种灾难和事件，破坏生态系统和污染，把地球变成一个无法生存的地狱！你需要使用点数尽力使人口归零，每回合使用不同的危机瓦解人类的团结！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/4ab7ae8173b58a851f5d4200cd00ebb6.poster.avif?t=1772080531\" width=616 height=150 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/4ab7ae8173b58a851f5d4200cd00ebb6.webm?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/4ab7ae8173b58a851f5d4200cd00ebb6.mp4?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/01349ec6024219f764718cc3422d8677.webp?t=1772080531\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为世界领袖，你拥有制定全球性法律和规定的权力，而其他玩家不一定会遵守这些规则，你需要在其他人作出自私选择的时候使用点数强制规范他们。你可能要面对不服从的工业界，拿着你筹集来的钱却没成果的科学家，恶劣影响的媒体和自私抗议的公众</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/17645f863badbd1b684943f6af13f1c4.poster.avif?t=1772080531\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/17645f863badbd1b684943f6af13f1c4.webm?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/17645f863badbd1b684943f6af13f1c4.mp4?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/0c1598a6301ba28a53a9194f6d5bb591.webp?t=1772080531\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为工业界的掌控者，是人类对于生态和污染平衡的唯一决定者，你更像是一个不可或缺的人类社会中转装置，需要使用自己的点数阻止地球对于生态污染的进一步恶化并且尽可能配合其他人的决定。你可能要面对压榨你点数的世界领袖，不断要钱的科学家，想尽一切曝光你的媒体和不愿配合的公众。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/99f2411b6313c333b90be668b0a88650.poster.avif?t=1772080531\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/99f2411b6313c333b90be668b0a88650.webm?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/99f2411b6313c333b90be668b0a88650.mp4?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/619a3ac1a8b3174809e21f1c9bfcde6d.webp?t=1772080531\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为科学家，你是拯救地球最关键的力量，你需要尽可能在每次研究时，投入你的点数或者寻求别人的帮助，找出让人类继续生存下去的方法。但你也会面对贪婪的领袖和工业界，落井下石的媒体还有公众的质疑。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/fb18aebfff5846bbb2c47967e7cec9d5.poster.avif?t=1772080531\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/fb18aebfff5846bbb2c47967e7cec9d5.webm?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/fb18aebfff5846bbb2c47967e7cec9d5.mp4?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/54e77b9ceb7587e8b12e5c44f226e043.webp?t=1772080531\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为媒体的代表，你是让普通人见证到世界真相的唯一途径，你需要使用自己的点数进行报道，将灾难来到的影响降到最低，你甚至还可以将其他人的决策颠倒黑白反转乾坤。但你可能要面对恼羞成怒的世界领袖，自私贪婪的工业界，毫无人道的科学家和不愿相信一切的公众</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/9709b3e0d73f77783b8d4e3c1492eb19.poster.avif?t=1772080531\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/9709b3e0d73f77783b8d4e3c1492eb19.webm?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/9709b3e0d73f77783b8d4e3c1492eb19.mp4?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/a3908170439c55ec637d97af445088ae.webp?t=1772080531\" width=616 height=48 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >最后一个角色是公众，代表着普通公民，作为地球上真正的主人，你决定着人类在灾难到来时如何抉择，你需要使用点数配合世界领袖所做出的决定，或者在灾难到来时进行自救。你可能要面对毫无作为的世界领袖，不断压榨的工业界，急于求成的科学家和夸大事实的媒体</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/d910842408e3114fa2ce3e00f6f56bc2.poster.avif?t=1772080531\" width=600 height=146 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/d910842408e3114fa2ce3e00f6f56bc2.webm?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2224610/extras/d910842408e3114fa2ce3e00f6f56bc2.mp4?t=1772080531\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《我不背锅》中，每个角色都有其独特的玩法和挑战。 既需要合作，又要追求自己的利益。最终，只能有一个胜者！准备好加入这场充满策略和挑战的游戏了吗？</p>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 简体中文<strong>*</strong>, 繁体中文<strong>*</strong>, 法语, 德语, 西班牙语 - 西班牙, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙, 俄语, 西班牙语 - 拉丁美洲, 日语<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
